subject: Fix the issue TIVI-1426: connman-test/simple-agent needs pygobject
commitMessage:
Fix the issue TIVI-1426: connman-test/simple-agent needs pygobject

platform/upstream/python-gobject and platform/upstream/pygobject2
use the same package name pygobject,
so change to "Provides: pygobject3"
